text: Debora Pixner (born 24 September 1992) is an Italian freestyle skier. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics, in ski cross. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Italy Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Merano Category:Germanophone Italian people
